    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the mince is browning, top, tail and chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Once the mince has browned, add the <strong>sliced courgette</strong> and cook for 3-4 min further or until the courgette has started to soften</p>",
