      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the ragù is cooking, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
