      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the potatoes to a low heat with a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Crumble in <strong>half</strong> your<strong> Greek cheese</strong> and add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>mint </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Mash until smooth then taste for seasoning, adding a pinch more <strong>salt</strong> if needed – this is your <strong>herby Greek cheese mash</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
